					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">&quot;Happened ever&quot; isn't exactly the same as &quot;was seen with any significant frequency&quot;<br /><br />&quot;Happened 3-4 times in an entire library of 1300-2000 games&quot; is awfully rare. More games used ROM nametables than had 4-screen RAM nametables, and we don't talk about them anywhere near as often.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

